      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities directly replicate the COU loading scenario (ASTM F1717 compression-bending) using production-representative hardware.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments replicate the COU loading modality (compression-bending per ASTM F1717) with production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated screws and UHMWPE test blocks. The FEA model is applied in the same configuration as the COU. Validation activity fidelity is high. Required level 3 achieved."
